scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 2-208 comprise the entire Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, starting with the heading 'SCHEDULE' and including all the 'Parts' (1-7) and their provisions. The text before line 2 is standard exhibit labeling, and after line 208 is a page break. There are no CSA annexes or standard pre-print sections within this span.
